From rocketchat.py line 454:

    def groups_info(self, room_id, **kwargs):
        """GRetrieves the information about the private group, only if you’re part of the group."""
        return self.__call_api_get('groups.info', roomId=room_id, kwargs=kwargs)

Above shows room_id as a required argument. The current rocketchat docs https://rocket.chat/docs/developer-guides/rest-api/groups/info/ require either roomId or roomName.

